node.text:
Marking 75 years since India's Independence. 

Freedom to me is freedom to fully express oneself, be oneself , all sides of oneself ... how else are we to ever find out our authentic selves! Let’s express fully , make those mistakes and grow... and so better ourselves , re invent ourselves. 

Courage to express fully is not easy. Harder still is the strength n humility to grow through our mistakes. 

So this Independence Day I wish for us all the strength and the freedom to ‘choose’ to be better individuals and a better nation . 

#happyindependenceday
